is to be the great American
fighting soldier...

1010
01:20:31,327 --> 01:20:34,037
that is inside each one of us.

1011
01:20:35,498 --> 01:20:37,415
Now, do what I do...

1012
01:20:39,460 --> 01:20:42,420
