No one! Not even the colonel!

1148
01:33:40,949 --> 01:33:42,199
Yes, sir.

1149
01:33:47,330 --> 01:33:49,832
You know, I think this guy
Stillman is really dangerous.

1150
01:33:50,000 --> 01:33:52,167
